data.description: NEW CONSTRUCTION ONE LEVEL HOME WITH ATTENTION TO DETAIL! Home features an open floorplan with vaulted ceilings in the kitchen dining and living room. Kitchen with white cabinetry with island, granite countertops and stainless appliances. Primary bedroom with en suite tiled bathroom with walk in shower and closet. Split bedroom plan with two additional bedrooms and a hall bathroom with bathtub and vanity with solid surface countertop. Separate laundry room, deck with a view of the large backyard and a two-car garage.
